This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: moon landing
des:
From the NASA archives, here are a few key moments from the Apollo 11 mission recollected through the audio tapes. Hear voices and noise from both Mission Control in Houston and the space craft.

Featured sections include:
- Lift-off
- Lunar landing
- First steps on the moon

Two special clips which can be found using the random function.
